r New\', Courier, mono, simsun, 宋体; width: 1079.625px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 17.65pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; color: teal; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">25</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt;\"><span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</span></span></span></pre><pre style=\"padding-top: 0px; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, mono, simsun, 宋体; width: 1079.625px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 17.65pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; color: teal; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">26</span></span></pre><pre style=\"padding-top: 0px; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, mono, simsun, 宋体; width: 1079.625px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 17.65pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; color: teal; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">27</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; color: blue; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">private</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; color: blue; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">native</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; color: blue; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">void</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\"> n_onCreate (android.os.Bundle p0);</span></span></pre><pre style=\"padding-top: 0px; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, mono, simsun, 宋体; width: 1079.625px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 17.65pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; color: teal; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">28</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt;\"> }</span></span></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　大家可以看到上面那个<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;native</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">n_onCreate</span>方法最后就会调用那个通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">mono</span>虚拟机注册的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mono.Samples.HelloWorld.OnCreate&nbsp;</span>方法。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Managed Callable Wrappers (MCW)</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　上面我们讲<span lang=\"EN-US\">Dalvik&nbsp;</span>虚拟机是我们<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>开发的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Android</span>应用程序的宿主，它通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">ACW</span>来调用我们用<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>写的方法。如果我们的这个<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>里面的方法涉及到一些声音或者系统本身，或者说现在已经有很多成熟的用<span lang=\"EN-US\">Java</span>写的类库，我们想调用怎么办？ 答案是我们再通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">MCW&nbsp;</span>调回去。在<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>运行时中去调用<span lang=\"EN-US\">Java&nbsp;</span>称之为<span lang=\"EN-US\">MCW</span>。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Xamarin.Android Framework</span>中有很多就是<span lang=\"EN-US\">MCW</span>，关于<span lang=\"EN-US\">MCW</span>的创建以及<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>与<span lang=\"EN-US\">Java</span>集成开发的东西我们后面再细讲，包括一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>开发的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Android</span>应用程序是如何被启动的，我们后面再细讲。对于<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>开发的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Android</span>应用程序来说，性能上面肯定是会有影响，但是影响有多大，我并没有做过具体测试，所以就不详述了。后面我们再细细的去对比。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Xamarin.IOS&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">架构</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　对于开发者来说，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Xamarin.IOS</span>相对于<span lang=\"EN-US\">Xamarin.Android</span>就要简单很多了，我们用<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>开发的<span lang=\"EN-US\">ios</span>应用程序在被编译成<span lang=\"EN-US\">IL</span>代码之后，然后转交给<span lang=\"EN-US\">Apple complier</span>直接编译成<span lang=\"EN-US\">IPhonee</span>的本地机器码。也就是说<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>写的<span lang=\"EN-US\">IPhone</span>应用程序和<span lang=\"EN-US\">objective-c&nbsp;</span>写的是一样的。并且<span lang=\"EN-US\">Xamarin</span>团队保证在每一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">IOS</span>系统更新的时间<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.cxyclub.cn/Tag/tongbu.html\" style=\"color: rgb(40, 127, 147); outline-style: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">同步</span></a></span>更新<span lang=\"EN-US\">Xamarin.IOS</span>这样我们就不用担心被滞后了。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">小结</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">　　这仅仅是一个粗略的介绍，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Xamarin</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">移动跨平台方案是如何来工作的，还有太多我们没有涉及。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;Xamarn.Forms</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">为多种移动平台提供了统一的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">UI</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">，当然在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Xamarin.Forms</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">不能够满足你的要求的时候，可以使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Xamarin.Android</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Xamarin.IOS</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">UI</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">控件，这些也是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Native</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">的，也就是说在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">UI</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">方面不会有性能的影响。</span></p><div class=\"Section1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　就目前来看<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>来开发<span lang=\"EN-US\">IOS</span>应用更具有优越性，我们要在<span lang=\"EN-US\">VS</span>中开发<span lang=\"EN-US\">Iphone</span>的应用程序需要配一台<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mac</span>来做编译。相对而言，开发<span lang=\"EN-US\">Android</span>的应用程序就会显得繁琐一些，底下还有一些隐藏的东西我们没有具体的讲，包括一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">app</span>的创建过程，<span lang=\"EN-US\">C#</span>与<span lang=\"EN-US\">Java</span>集成在一起开发时候的交互等等，这些问题我们就留在后面慢慢来解决。</span></p></div></div>', ' Xamarin 原理   微软宣布了开放.NET框架源代码并且会为Windows、Mac和Linux开发一个核心运行时（Core CLR），这也是开源的！IT媒体网站纷纷转载，博客园的C#开发者们热泪盈眶 与此同时VS2015预览版更是直接集成了Android模拟器，但是其实里面并没有说集成IOS模拟器，我不知道大家是怎么得出可以直接用VS来开发Android和IOS应用的。不管怎么说，这都是个好消息。那么问题来了，C#如何来开发Android和IOS应用？微软会怎么做我们不确定，但是我们倒是可以来看看Xamarin是如何做的。Android 体系架构：我想下面这张图Android 开发的同学应该很熟悉，下面我们就通过来了解Android系统的架构入门来看看Xamarin会怎么样去做？ 现在做Android开发的同学只要熟悉这些应用框架层的一些接口和类库就可以给方便的来实现自己的Android应用程序。Dalvk虚拟机与Java运行环境的区别：   1、Dalvik主要是完成对象生命周期管理，堆栈管理，线程管理，安全和异常管理，以及垃圾回收等等重要功能。  2、Dalvik负责进程隔离和线程管理，每一个Android应用在底层都会对应一个独立的Dalvik虚拟机实例，其代码在虚拟机的解释下得以执行。  3、不同于Java虚拟机运行java字节码，Dalvik虚拟机运行的是其专有的文件格式  4、Dex文件格式可以减少整体文件尺寸，提高I/o操作的类查找速度。是为了在运行过程中进一步提高性能，对dex文件的进一步优化。  5、所有的Android应用的线程都对应一个Linux线程，虚拟机因而可以更多的依赖操作系统的线程调度和管理机制，有一个特殊的虚拟机进程Zygote，他是虚拟机实例的孵化器。它在系统启动', '', null, '2015-03-09 23:55:40', 'song,2015-04-24 20:43:48', '', '49.84.117.65', '0', '826', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('27', '', '1', '8', '开发,IOS', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', '苹果开发者账号申请（个人）流程【5】', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 173%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">苹果开发者账号申请（个人）流程</span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">准备：</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、具有国际支付能力的银行卡一张<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>卡上带有<span lang=\"EN-US\">VISA</span>标志或者<span lang=\"EN-US\">MasterCard</span>标志<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、一个已经注册的苹果设备<span lang=\"EN-US\">ID(Apple ID</span>，相信有苹果设备的人都有<span lang=\"EN-US\">Apple ID)</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">流程：</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、登陆苹果开发者申请网站（<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/programs/ios/\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">https://developer.apple.com/programs/ios/</span></b></a></span></span>）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt;\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/7wft8y_苹果设备越狱19.png\" width=\"557\" height=\"445\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> 2</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">、点击 <span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;enroll&quot;</span>进入注册说明页。了解一下官方给出的注册说明，点击<span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;continue&quot;</span>之后正式进入注册流程：</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、选择使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">Existing Apple ID&nbsp; Sign In</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、选择注册类型：<span lang=\"EN-US\">Individual(</span>个人<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、选择购买开发方向，<b><span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">不会选择不要瞎选择，<span lang=\"EN-US\">IOS Developer </span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mac Developer </span>是两个独立产品，独立收费，在这里开发<span lang=\"EN-US\">IOS</span>只需要将<span lang=\"EN-US\">IOS Developer</span>即可，本人当时也不知道，都选择了，到后面的步骤发现需要花费<span lang=\"EN-US\">198$</span>才发现自己选择错了，但是苹果这点做的很恶心，没法回退重新选择，只能打电话给苹果客服取消。</span></b></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/p8pa7x_苹果设备越狱16.png\" width=\"864\" height=\"540\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、填写个人信息（<a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1wFKFs\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><b>中国地址的英文书写格式<span lang=\"EN-US\">.doc</span></b></span></a>）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/vyg2fp_苹果设备越狱17.png\" width=\"701\" height=\"681\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、设置银行卡信息<b><span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">（划款不需要密码验证与Apple ID 绑定，谨慎保管Apple ID及密码）</span>。</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、设置发票信息。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、确认完成付款，完成开发者账号的配置。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/rbvwj5_苹果设备越狱18.png\" width=\"643\" height=\"607\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 10</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">XCode </span>—<span lang=\"EN-US\">Preferences</span>—<span lang=\"EN-US\">Accounts</span>添加<span lang=\"EN-US\">Apple ID</span>查看权限</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/nat8jp_苹果设备越狱20.png\" width=\"772\" height=\"462\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>', '苹果开发者账号申请（个人）流程准备：1、具有国际支付能力的银行卡一张(卡上带有VISA标志或者MasterCard标志)2、一个已经注册的苹果设备ID(Apple ID，相信有苹果设备的人都有Apple ID)流程：  1、登陆苹果开发者申请网站（https://developer.apple.com/programs/ios/）        2、点击 &quot;enroll&quot;进入注册说明页。了解一下官方给出的注册说明，点击&quot;continue&quot;之后正式进入注册流程：  3、选择使用Existing Apple ID  Sign In  4、选择注册类型：Individual(个人)  5、选择购买开发方向，不会选择不要瞎选择，IOS Developer 和Mac Developer 是两个独立产品，独立收费，在这里开发IOS只需要将IOS Developer即可，本人当时也不知道，都选择了，到后面的步骤发现需要花费198$才发现自己选择错了，但是苹果这点做的很恶心，没法回退重新选择，只能打电话给苹果客服取消。  6、填写个人信息（中国地址的英文书写格式.doc）  7、设置银行卡信息（划款不需要密码验证与Apple ID 绑定，谨慎保管Apple ID及密码）。  8、设置发票信息。  9、确认完成付款，完成开发者账号的配置。    10通过XCode —Preferences—Accounts添加Apple ID查看权限', '', null, '2015-03-10 23:03:17', 'song,2015-03-11 00:16:04', '', '101.40.52.42', '0', '839', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('28', '', '1', '11', '', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', '时间都去哪了【1】', '<p style=\"font: 12px/normal Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">时间都去哪了</span></b></p><p style=\"font: 12px/normal Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;貌似这是一个老生常谈的话题，对于这个话题，相信人人都能说出一堆自己的牢骚，发出自己的叹息，高中毕业的时候，说时间过得好快，小学、初中一下就过去了，自己已经十八岁了，已经成年了；大学毕业的时候，说时间过得好快，自己已经不再是一个学生，已经步如社会，要自己出去谋生计，补贴家里了，如今工作四年了，说时间过得好快，到谈婚论嫁的年龄，要结婚养小孩，养育自己的下一代，开始我们吾辈的循环了，回想这二十多年的过去，真的想问一句，时间都去哪了，还没怎么经历、还没什么收获、还没怎么享受！！！！</span></p><div style=\"font: 12px/normal Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;想想自己工作的这几年，从当时公司最年轻的程序员，到如今，公司资历最老的程序员，从领导口中的小宋到入境的老宋，从同事口中的“宋”，到后来的“宋哥”，再到现在的“宋爷”，估计再过一两年，又会变成“宋大爷”吧。</span></div><p style=\"font: 12px/normal Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img width=\"660\" height=\"376\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/qrreza_生活随想0.png\" /></p><p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span>年小学照片）</span></p><p style=\"font: 12px/normal Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img width=\"660\" height=\"376\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/awu4y0_生活随想1.png\" /></p><p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span>年高中照片）</span></p><p style=\"font: 12px/normal Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img width=\"689\" height=\"480\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1503/ee1c4t_生活随想2.png\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年工作照片）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>', ' 时间都去哪了   貌似这是一个老生常谈的话题，对于这个话题，相信人人都能说出一堆自己的牢骚，发出自己的叹息，高中毕业的时候，说时间过得好快，小学、初中一下就过去了，自己已经十八岁了，已经成年了；大学毕业的时候，说时间过得好快，自己已经不再是一个学生，已经步如社会，要自己出去谋生计，补贴家里了，如今工作四年了，说时间过得好快，到谈婚论嫁的年龄，要结婚养小孩，养育自己的下一代，开始我们吾辈的循环了，回想这二十多年的过去，真的想问一句，时间都去哪了，还没怎么经历、还没什么收获、还没怎么享受！！！！ 想想自己工作的这几年，从当时公司最年轻的程序员，到如今，公司资历最老的程序员，从领导口中的小宋到入境的老宋，从同事口中的“宋”，到后来的“宋哥”，再到现在的“宋爷”，估计再过一两年，又会变成“宋大爷”吧。（2001年小学照片）（2007年高中照片）（2011年工作照片）', '', null, '2015-03-16 23:20:49', 'song,2015-04-04 15:19:02', '', '101.41.107.8', '0', '464', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('29', '', '1', '11', '', '\0', '\0', '', '\0', '时间改变了我们【2】', '<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background: white; color: #333333; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “买房”，“结婚”这些在当年学生时代被各种戳之以鼻的名词，到如今，都一个一个变成了现实，一个一个困扰着我们这个阶段，以前说我以后不买房，要和爸妈住在一块，要孝顺爸妈，现在呢，要成立自己的家庭，要养育自己的小孩，让自己的小孩从小接受好的教育，避免走我们的老路，各种学区房层出不穷，各种抢购，为了买一套好点的房子，不惜榨干父母多年的血汗，父母供养自己上完小学，上完初中、上完高中、上完大学，甚至上完研究生，还要掏出养老金给自己买房子；以前说我以后不结婚，要当和尚或者说要在家陪爸妈一辈子的话再也提听不到了，反而是因为结婚偏向媳妇，和爸妈各种吵闹，更有甚者，甚至引起父母老年病复发，直接进医院，把当年父亲的背影，母亲手中线，一步一步把你从家送到火车站，一针一针给你织补冬天的毛衣的情形跑到脑后，把爸妈的辛劳当成了义务，把孝顺父母的义务当成了享受父母的权利。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background: white; color: #333333; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background: white; color: #333333; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">工作了四年，回想过去的点点滴滴，父母能把我们供养到大学毕业，已经完成了他们那一代的使命了，我们应该感谢他们，那些读硕士、博士的更应该感谢他们，能大学毕业，父母已经给我们超支很多了，不要再去榨取他们的养老的本钱了，作为一个大学生、研究生、博士生，为什么没有人站出来说一句：我赚多少，我用多少，我赚多少，我买多大的房，我赚多少，我结什么级别的婚？<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>', '  “买房”，“结婚”这些在当年学生时代被各种戳之以鼻的名词，到如今，都一个一个变成了现实，一个一个困扰着我们这个阶段，以前说我以后不买房，要和爸妈住在一块，要孝顺爸妈，现在呢，要成立自己的家庭，要养育自己的小孩，让自己的小孩从小接受好的教育，避免走我们的老路，各种学区房层出不穷，各种抢购，为了买一套好点的房子，不惜榨干父母多年的血汗，父母供养自己上完小学，上完初中、上完高中、上完大学，甚至上完研究生，还要掏出养老金给自己买房子；以前说我以后不结婚，要当和尚或者说要在家陪爸妈一辈子的话再也提听不到了，反而是因为结婚偏向媳妇，和爸妈各种吵闹，更有甚者，甚至引起父母老年病复发，直接进医院，把当年父亲的背影，母亲手中线，一步一步把你从家送到火车站，一针一针给你织补冬天的毛衣的情形跑到脑后，把爸妈的辛劳当成了义务，把孝顺父母的义务当成了享受父母的权利。  工作了四年，回想过去的点点滴滴，父母能把我们供养到大学毕业，已经完成了他们那一代的使命了，我们应该感谢他们，那些读硕士、博士的更应该感谢他们，能大学毕业，父母已经给我们超支很多了，不要再去榨取他们的养老的本钱了，作为一个大学生、研究生、博士生，为什么没有人站出来说一句：我赚多少，我用多少，我赚多少，我买多大的房，我赚多少，我结什么级别的婚？', '', null, '2015-03-16 23:32:08', 'song,2015-03-16 23:39:50', '', '101.40.75.190', '0', '618', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('30', '', '1', '13', 'App,移动版', '\0', '\0', '\0', '', '宋爷 de Life 安卓移动App上线了', '<p><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><b><font face=\"宋体\">宋爷 de Life移动版App上线了!!!!!!!</font></b></span></p><p><b>Apk下载地址： &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1ntmQKlF\" target=\"_blank\"><u><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">宋爷 de Life.Apk</span></b></u></a></b></p><p><b>Apk源码下载地址： </b><a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1dDq4JAT\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">WebApp.rar(Xamarin C# 版)</span></b></a></p><p><b><img width=\"176\" height=\"205\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/at4pmt_宋爷delife.png\" /></b></p>', '宋爷 de Life移动版App上线了!!!!!!!Apk下载地址：        宋爷 de Life.ApkApk源码下载地址： WebApp.rar(Xamarin C# 版)', '', null, '2015-04-01 12:06:49', 'song,2015-04-04 17:04:08', '', '101.41.107.8', '0', '784', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('32', '', '1', '14', 'ArcGIS,插件', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'ArcMap（Desktop）插件开发', '<p>&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 173%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">ArcMap</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 173%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Desktop</span>）插件开发</span></h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 前两天老领导安排一个事情，说是之前做了一个添加自定义瓦片的数据的功能，集成到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcMap </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">里面使用，可是之前用的是北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">54 </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的坐标系，而且集成环境是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcGIS 10.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，现在用户想添加一个北京本地坐标系的瓦片，并且要集成到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcGIS 10.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上，当时开发功能的同事不在公司了，哎，艰巨的任务又落到了我的身上，老领导的任务没有不着急的，还安排一个小姑娘跟着我后面盯着，没办法，干吧，倒持了半天，百度</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">谷歌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+ESRI</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客服，一通乱搜、乱找，终于在下班前搞定，给了小姑娘教会了用户，总结如下：</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcEngine </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">开发</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcGIS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">插件有两种方式，一种创建绑定库类型工程，一个通过创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Add In</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">类型工程，通过创建绑定库类型工程支持</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcMap9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以上版本，而通过创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Add In</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">类型工程只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcEngine10.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">版本后才支持，毫无疑问，选择第一种方式</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ArcGIS Desktop</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工程，通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">VS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">新建工程，选择</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ArcGIS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">模块下面的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Class library(Desktop)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，一般正确安装</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ArcEngine ,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">都会在新建工程面板中多了一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ArcGIS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">模块</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/dco13f_GIS开发1.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"426\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、创建添加瓦片数据工具，通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">VS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">添加新文件，选择</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcGIS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">模块下面的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BaseTool</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BaseCommand</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">类型，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Command </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tool </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有什么区别，主要是看是否和地图有鼠标或者键盘的交互，此次不和地图交互，所有选择的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BaseCommand</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">类型</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/qgnq3r_GIS开发2.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"359\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、添加对应</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcGIS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcEngine</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">库的应用，这个主要看功能的逻辑，需要调用什么库就添加什么库。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Command</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的一些基本属性，例如分组、名称、图标、描述信息等，使用方法同</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcEngine </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tool</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Command</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">相同。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、完成瓦片数据添加的业务逻辑，这里可以通过打开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">文件，在文件中右键，通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcGIS Snippet Finder</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">菜单，弹出快速搜索的面板，对所需要的参数如何获取或者如何使用进行快速检索</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/i3jm94_GIS开发3.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"447\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 这里列举常用参数的获取方式：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过重写</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun; color: blue;\">void</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\"> OnCreate(<span style=\"color: blue;\">object</span> hook)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方法获取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">hook</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对象</span></span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-c\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;OnCreate(</span><span class=\"keyword\">object</span><span>&nbsp;hook)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span><span>&nbsp;(hook&nbsp;!=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;var&nbsp;hookhelper&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;HookHelperClass();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;hookhelper.Hook&nbsp;=&nbsp;hook;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;var&nbsp;application&nbsp;=&nbsp;hook&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">as</span><span>&nbsp;IApplication;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li></ol></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">hookhelper </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">获取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ActiveView </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">FocusedMap</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">Pagelayout</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对象，拿到需要参数后，直接通过操作对象完成对应的业务逻辑开发。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、工具完整代码摘抄如下：</span></span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-c\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"keyword\">    using</span><span>&nbsp;ESRI.ArcGIS;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;ESRI.ArcGIS.ADF.BaseClasses;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;ESRI.ArcGIS.ADF.CATIDs;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;ESRI.ArcGIS.ArcMapUI;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;ESRI.ArcGIS.Carto;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;ESRI.ArcGIS.Controls;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;ESRI.ArcGIS.Framework;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;System;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;System.Diagnostics;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;System.Drawing;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;System.Runtime.InteropServices;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">using</span><span>&nbsp;System.Windows.Forms;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[ProgId(<span class=\"string\">&quot;DesktopClassLibrary1.AddTileData&quot;</span><span>),&nbsp;ClassInterface(ClassInterfaceType.None),&nbsp;Guid(</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;ec5ea54c-0b09-418d-b215-d2ec607302b6&quot;</span><span>)]&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">sealed</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">class</span><span>&nbsp;AddTileData&nbsp;:&nbsp;BaseCommand&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;IApplication&nbsp;m_application;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;IHookHelper&nbsp;m_hookHelper&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;IActiveView&nbsp;m_pActiveView;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;AddTileData()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;RuntimeManager.Bind(ProductCode.EngineOrDesktop);&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_category&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;ForeStar&quot;</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_caption&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;添加瓦片数据&quot;</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_message&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;添加瓦片数据&quot;</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_toolTip&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;添加瓦片数据&quot;</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_name&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;ForeStar_AddTileData&quot;</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">try</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">string</span><span>&nbsp;resource&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.GetType().Name&nbsp;+&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;.bmp&quot;</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_bitmap&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;Bitmap(</span><span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.GetType(),&nbsp;resource);&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">catch</span><span>&nbsp;(Exception&nbsp;exception)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Trace.WriteLine(exception.Message,&nbsp;<span class=\"string\">&quot;Invalid&nbsp;Bitmap&quot;</span><span>);&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">static</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;ArcGISCategoryRegistration(System.Type&nbsp;registerType)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;MxCommands.Register(<span class=\"keyword\">string</span><span>.Format(@</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\\CLSID\\{{{0}}}&quot;</span><span>,&nbsp;registerType.GUID));&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">static</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;ArcGISCategoryUnregistration(System.Type&nbsp;registerType)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;MxCommands.Unregister(<span class=\"keyword\">string</span><span>.Format(@</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\\CLSID\\{{{0}}}&quot;</span><span>,&nbsp;registerType.GUID));&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">override</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;OnClick()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">this</span><span>.m_pActiveView&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">this</span><span>.m_hookHelper.ActiveView;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;FolderBrowserDialog&nbsp;dialog&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;FolderBrowserDialog&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Description&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"string\">&quot;添¬¨ª加¨®瓦ª?片?数ºy据Y&quot;</span><span>,&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ShowNewFolderButton&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">false</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;};&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">if</span><span>&nbsp;(dialog.ShowDialog()&nbsp;==&nbsp;DialogResult.OK)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;IMapZoneWNTSMapLayer&nbsp;layer&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;MapZoneWNTSMapLayer(1,&nbsp;dialog.SelectedPath);&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ILayer&nbsp;layer2&nbsp;=&nbsp;layer;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">this</span><span>.m_pActiveView.FocusMap.AddLayer(layer2);&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">this</span><span>.m_pActiveView.Refresh();&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">override</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;OnCreate(</span><span class=\"keyword\">object</span><span>&nbsp;hook)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">if</span><span>&nbsp;(hook&nbsp;!=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">this</span><span>.m_hookHelper&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;HookHelperClass();&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">this</span><span>.m_hookHelper.Hook&nbsp;=&nbsp;hook;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">this</span><span>.m_application&nbsp;=&nbsp;hook&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">as</span><span>&nbsp;IApplication;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">if</span><span>&nbsp;(hook&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">is</span><span>&nbsp;IMxApplication)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_enabled&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">true</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">base</span><span>.m_enabled&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">false</span><span>;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[ComRegisterFunction,&nbsp;ComVisible(<span class=\"keyword\">false</span><span>)]&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">static</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;RegisterFunction(System.Type&nbsp;registerType)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ArcGISCategoryRegistration(registerType);&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[ComUnregisterFunction,&nbsp;ComVisible(<span class=\"keyword\">false</span><span>)]&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">static</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;UnregisterFunction(System.Type&nbsp;registerType)&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ArcGISCategoryUnregistration(registerType);&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li></ol></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、调试</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ArcGIS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工具</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）设置通过外部工程启动调试，外部程序路径选择</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ArcMap</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">程序所在路径，例如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">C:\\Program Files (x86)\\ArcGIS\\Desktop10.2\\bin\\</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ArcMap.exe</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/0p5lzs_GIS开发4.png\" width=\"629\" height=\"445\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\nNSimSun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-bidi-font-family:NSimSun;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\"> 2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">设置工程版本为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">.Net Framework3.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，此处折腾我半天，调试死活不进断点，没办法，想起我们</span></span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还有伟大的技术客服，直接给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ESRI</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客服打电话，一句话解决了我的困扰，我用的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">VS2010</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">搭建的开发环境，新建的工程</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">.net FrameWork</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">版本默认为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">4.0</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">版，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ArcGIS10.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">默认支持的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">.Net Framework3.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">版本，如果想要调试</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">4.0</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的程序，需要进行一堆复杂的设置，为了节省时间，我选择了将程序工程为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">.Net Framework3.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，这个是和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ArcGIS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">版本有关，不同版本默认支持的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">.Net </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">版本不一样，需要百度</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">+</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">谷歌或者给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ESRI</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客服打电话，将工程调整成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">3.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">后，立杆见影、果断进断点，各种高兴啊，问题终于解决了，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">各种无奈啊，用人家的东西只能遵守人家的规则。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）运行，启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">ArcMap</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">程序（移植到其他电脑只要和下面的操作相同）</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）添加工具到菜单中，选择自定义—自定义模式</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/qq3afh_GIS开发5.png\" width=\"403\" height=\"299\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\nNSimSun;mso-bidi-font-family:NSimSun;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: NSimSun;\"> &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从文件添加</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/m9w9pn_GIS开发6.png\" width=\"413\" height=\"350\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">选择以</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">.tlb</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结尾的文件进行添加，如果有对应的工具，则会给出对应的提示：</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/521n5e_GIS开发7.png\" width=\"571\" height=\"436\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">找到对应的工具，并给出提示</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/lwbt34_GIS开发8.png\" width=\"285\" height=\"213\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在自定义工具的命令页，通过关键字搜索，找到对应的工具，拖拽到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ArcMap</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的菜单中（这个步骤教了用户半天都不会用，这个我也不好说什么了）</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/ayf6v6_GIS开发10.png\" width=\"417\" height=\"354\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/t31kzp_GIS开发9.png\" width=\"565\" height=\"190\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">给用户部署使用，只要按照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）进行安装即可</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">参考地址：</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><a href=\"http://resources.arcgis.com/en/help/arcobjects-net/conceptualhelp/index.html#//0001000004n5000000\" target=\"_blank\">方法一参考</a></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://resources.arcgis.com/en/help/arcobjects-net/conceptualhelp/index.html#/Building_add_ins_for_ArcGIS_for_Desktop/0001000000w2000000/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">方法二参考</span></a></p>', ' ArcMap（Desktop）插件开发    前两天老领导安排一个事情，说是之前做了一个添加自定义瓦片的数据的功能，集成到ArcMap 里面使用，可是之前用的是北京54 的坐标系，而且集成环境是ArcGIS 10.1，现在用户想添加一个北京本地坐标系的瓦片，并且要集成到ArcGIS 10.2上，当时开发功能的同事不在公司了，哎，艰巨的任务又落到了我的身上，老领导的任务没有不着急的，还安排一个小姑娘跟着我后面盯着，没办法，干吧，倒持了半天，百度+谷歌+ESRI客服，一通乱搜、乱找，终于在下班前搞定，给了小姑娘教会了用户，总结如下： 通过ArcEngine 开发ArcGIS插件有两种方式，一种创建绑定库类型工程，一个通过创建Add In类型工程，通过创建绑定库类型工程支持ArcMap9以上版本，而通过创建Add In类型工程只有ArcEngine10.1版本后才支持，毫无疑问，选择第一种方式       1、创建ArcGIS Desktop工程，通过VS新建工程，选择ArcGIS模块下面的Class library(Desktop)，一般正确安装ArcEngine ,都会在新建工程面板中多了一个ArcGIS模块      2、创建添加瓦片数据工具，通过VS添加新文件，选择ArcGIS模块下面的BaseTool或者BaseCommand类型，Command 和Tool 有什么区别，主要是看是否和地图有鼠标或者键盘的交互，此次不和地图交互，所有选择的是BaseCommand类型        3、添加对应ArcGIS、ArcEngine库的应用，这个主要看功能的逻辑，需要调用什么库就添加什么库。        4、设置Command的一些基本属性，例如分组、名称、图标、描述信息等，使用方法同ArcEngine 创建Tool和Command相同。        5、完成瓦片数据添加的业务逻辑，这里可以通过打开CS文件，在文件中右键，通过ArcGIS Snippet ', '', null, '2015-04-04 16:47:15', 'song,2015-04-06 10:41:34', '', '101.40.94.31', '0', '1014', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('33', '', '1', '13', '', '\0', '\0', '\0', '', '宋爷 de Life 苹果移动App上线了', '<p>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Article/30.aspx\" class=\"ArticleList.TitleClass\" style=\"color: rgb(40, 127, 147); font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;\" target=\"_blank\">宋爷 de Life 苹果移动App上线了</a></p><p><b style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; text-align: justify;\">App名称：</b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><b style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; text-align: justify;\">宋爷 de Life</b></span></p><p><b style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; text-align: justify;\">App源码</b>：<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1qWLXuUS\" target=\"_blank\">http://pan.baidu.com/s/1qWLXuUS</a></span></p><p>网站上提越狱信息都不给过，苹果太啃跌了</p><p><b style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/vqsp06_宋爷网站10.png\" width=\"282\" height=\"288\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></b></p>', ' 宋爷 de Life 苹果移动App上线了App名称：宋爷 de LifeApp源码：http://pan.baidu.com/s/1qWLXuUS网站上提越狱信息都不给过，苹果太啃跌了', '', null, '2015-04-24 13:47:20', 'song,2015-07-18 09:50:01', '', '180.213.73.45', '0', '635', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('34', '', '1', '13', '', '\0', '\0', '\0', '', '宋爷 de Life 微软移动App', '<p>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Article/30.aspx\" class=\"ArticleList.TitleClass\" style=\"color: rgb(40, 127, 147); font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px;\" target=\"_blank\">宋爷 de Life 微软移动App</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px; text-align: justify;\"><b>App名称：</b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><b>宋爷 de Life</b></span></p><p><b style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px; text-align: justify;\">App源码</b><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px; text-align: justify;\">：</span><font face=\"Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px;\"><a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/12heqy\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">http://pan.baidu.com/s/12heqy</span></b></a></span></font></p><p><img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1504/59ltja_宋爷网站11.png\" width=\"533\" height=\"288\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p>', ' 宋爷 de Life 微软移动AppApp名称：宋爷 de LifeApp源码：http://pan.baidu.com/s/12heqy', '', null, '2015-04-24 14:17:37', 'song,2015-04-24 14:25:54', '', '58.218.185.70', '0', '581', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('35', '', '1', '16', '', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'C#转JavaScript坑', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">写习惯了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">c# </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的代码，转向其他语言，难免会遇到各种各样的不习惯，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">c#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">语言的简单化、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">VS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">开发环境的方便性</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">带给我们好多方便的同时也让我们在转向其他的开发语言、其他的开发环境，会感觉很不适应，会各种吐槽问题，最近在写</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JavaScript </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">代码的时候解决一个问题让我苦笑不得，特贴出来与大家分享，避免大家陷入和我同样的问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">一般写</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">c# </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">代码，对于花括号都习惯于换行输出，即好看又工整，还方便查错，但是在写</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JavaScript</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的时候，就会容易出问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-c\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">class</span><span>&nbsp;Test&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;TestMethod()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;MessageBox.Show(“Hello&nbsp;Word!”);&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>}&nbsp;</span></li></ol></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">上面的方法在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C# </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">语法中不会存在任何问题，但是下面的方法，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JavaScript </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">中运行就会报错，查找了一晚上，发现不是函数问题、不是语法问题，问题出在花括号的位置上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-c\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"keyword\">var</span><span>&nbsp;shopindex&nbsp;=&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"keyword\">function</span><span>()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">var</span><span>&nbsp;start&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">function</span><span>()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;alert();&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">return</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;start:&nbsp;start&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>})()&nbsp;</span></li></ol></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;color:#3E4B53;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-no-proof:yes\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"><o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"></o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"图片_x0020_48\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:360.75pt;height:180pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"跨语言问题1\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;\ncolor:#3E4B53;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p><pre style=\"width: 1141.46875px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Consolas; color: rgb(62, 75, 83);\">上面代码在浏览器运行的时候报<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Uncaught TypeError:Cannot read property \'start\' of undefined</span></b></span></span></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;\ncolor:#3E4B53;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">将代码修改成如下格式后，在浏览器中就能正常通过</span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-c\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"keyword\">var</span><span>&nbsp;shopindex&nbsp;=&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"keyword\">function</span><span>()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">var</span><span>&nbsp;start&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">function</span><span>()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;alert();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">return</span><span>{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;start:&nbsp;start&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>})()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li></ol></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">问题出在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">renturn</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">后面的花括号位置问题，换行输出报错，紧随</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">renturn</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">之后顺利执行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;这个结果让我有点哭笑不得，问了一下度娘，得<b>知<span style=\"color:red\">浏览器在执行的时候会在非特定条件下（例如方法名后面、</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">for</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\ncolor:red\">循环后面，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">while</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\ncolor:red\">循环后面），如果某行代码没有分号结束标识，会自动补全</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，很不幸上述代码的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">return </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">不属于特定条件，被浏览器自定补加了一个分号，导致程序执行的时候，提示</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">start</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">未定义。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>', '写习惯了c# 的代码，转向其他语言，难免会遇到各种各样的不习惯，c#语言的简单化、VS开发环境的方便性带给我们好多方便的同时也让我们在转向其他的开发语言、其他的开发环境，会感觉很不适应，会各种吐槽问题，最近在写JavaScript 代码的时候解决一个问题让我苦笑不得，特贴出来与大家分享，避免大家陷入和我同样的问题。一般写c# 代码，对于花括号都习惯于换行输出，即好看又工整，还方便查错，但是在写JavaScript的时候，就会容易出问题。   public class Test { public void TestMethod() { MessageBox.Show(“Hello Word!”); } } 上面的方法在C# 语法中不会存在任何问题，但是下面的方法，在JavaScript 中运行就会报错，查找了一晚上，发现不是函数问题、不是语法问题，问题出在花括号的位置上。var shopindex = (function() { var start = function() { alert(); } return { start: start } })() 上面代码在浏览器运行的时候报Uncaught TypeError:Cannot read property \'start\' of undefined将代码修改成如下格式后，在浏览器中就能正常通过var shopindex = (function() { var start = function() { alert(); } return{ start: start } })() 问题出在renturn后面的花括号位置问题，换行输出报错，紧随renturn之后顺利执行。     这个结果让我有点哭笑不得，问了一下度娘，得知浏览器在执行的时候会在非特定条件下（例如方法名后面、for循环后面，while循环后面），如果某行代码没有分号结束标识，会自动补全，很不幸上述代码的return 不属于特定条件，被浏览器自定补加了一个分号，导致程序执行的时候，提示start未定义。', '', null, '2015-07-17 22:19:14', 'song,2015-07-18 09:49:44', '', '180.213.73.45', '0', '439', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('36', '', '1', '10', 'AndroidStudio,版本', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Android Studio 开发android 版本问题', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">Error:(23, 13) Failed to resolve: com.android.support:appcompat-v7:22.+</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">解决方法：</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第一、查看对应</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SDKManager </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Extras </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Android Support Library </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">版本，如果没有请先下载</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第二、根据下载版本，修改对应工程文件的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">app\\build.gradle </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">文件中对应的版本信息，修改内容包括：</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 54pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">）<span lang=\"EN-US\">dependencies {<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; compile fileTree(</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\ncolor:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">dir</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">: </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\n宋体;color:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">\'libs\'</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">, </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">include</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">: [</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:green;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\'*.jar\'</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">])<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; compile </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:green;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\'com.android.support:appcompat-v7:22.+\'<br /></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">}</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 54pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">compile</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">后面</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">v7:22 </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:green;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">其中 <span lang=\"EN-US\">v7 </span>代表支持库<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 22</span>代表对应版本，根据自己安装版本修改数字即可</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: 4.5pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">）<span lang=\"EN-US\">android {<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; compileSdkVersion </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\ncolor:blue;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">19<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">buildToolsVersion </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:green;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&quot;19.1.0&quot;<br /><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">defaultConfig {<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; applicationId </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\ncolor:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&quot;min.gwsc&quot;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">minSdkVersion </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">8<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">targetSdkVersion </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">19<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">versionCode </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">versionName </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&quot;1.0&quot;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">}</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 54pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">修改<span lang=\"EN-US\">compileSdkVersion</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">buildToolsVersion</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">targetSdkVersion</span>版本与本地安装版本对应</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">google</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">提供了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Android Support Library package </span><span style=\"font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">系列的包来保证来高版本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sdk</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">开发的向下兼容性，即我们用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.x</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">开发时，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">等版本上，可以使用高版本的有些特性，如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">fragement,ViewPager</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">等，下面，简单说明下这几个版本间的区别：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Android Support v4:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">这个包是为了照顾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">及更高版本而设计的，这个包是使用最广泛的，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">eclipse</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">新建工程时，都默认带有了。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Android Support v7:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">这个包是为了考虑照顾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">及以上版本而设计的，但不包含更低，故如果不考虑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.6,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">我们可以采用再加上这个包，另外注意，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">v7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">是要依赖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">v4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">这个包的，即，两个得同时被包含。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Android Support v13&nbsp; :</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">这个包的设计是为了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">android 3.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">及更高版本的，一般我们都不常用，平板开发中能用到。</span></p>', ' Error:(23, 13) Failed to resolve: com.android.support:appcompat-v7:22.+解决方法：第一、查看对应SDKManager 中Extras 下Android Support Library 版本，如果没有请先下载第二、根据下载版本，修改对应工程文件的app\\build.gradle 文件中对应的版本信息，修改内容包括：1）dependencies {   compile fileTree(dir: \'libs\', include: [\'*.jar\'])   compile \'com.android.support:appcompat-v7:22.+\'}compile后面v7:22 其中 v7 代表支持库 22代表对应版本，根据自己安装版本修改数字即可2）android {   compileSdkVersion 19   buildToolsVersion &quot;19.1.0&quot;   defaultConfig {   applicationId &quot;min.gwsc&quot;   minSdkVersion 8   targetSdkVersion 19   versionCode 1   versionName &quot;1.0&quot;   }修改compileSdkVersion、buildToolsVersion、targetSdkVersion版本与本地安装版本对应google提供了Android Support Library package 系列的包来保证来高版本sdk开发的向下兼容性，即我们用4.x开发时，在1.6等版本上，可以使用高版本的有些特性，如fragement,ViewPager等，下面，简单说明下这几个版本间的区别： Android Support v4: 这个包是为了照顾1.6及更高版本而设计的，这个包是使用最广泛的，eclipse新建工程时，都默认带有了。Android Support v7: 这个包是为了考虑照顾2.1及以上版本而设计的，但不包含更低，故如果不考虑1.6,我们可以采用再加上这个包，另外注意，v7是要依赖v4这个包的，即，两个得同时被包含。Android Support v13  :这个包的设计是为了android 3.2及更高版本的，一般我们都不常用，平板开发中能用到。', '', null, '2015-07-23 15:15:44', 'song,2015-08-05 15:16:05', '', '180.213.186.130', '0', '3837', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('37', '', '1', '10', 'AndroidStudio', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Android Studio 编译Failed to notify project evaluation listener 问题', '<p>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Android Studio </span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">中对外部工程的概念不叫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Proejct </span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">了，而是将外部工程当成一个模块引入到当前工程中，定义为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Module</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在导入的外部</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Module </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">多了，进行编译，难免会遇到各种各样的问题，今天编译的时候就遇到了如下的问题</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">Error:A problem occurred configuring project \':app\'.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">&gt; Failed to notify project evaluation listener.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &gt; java.lang.StackOverflowError (no error message)</span></p><pre style=\"background:white\">\n找了半天，原来是<span lang=\"EN-US\">Module</span>过了，导致了<span lang=\"EN-US\">Module</span>之间的循环引用问题，知道了问题的原因所在，解决起来就快了，查找每个<span lang=\"EN-US\">Module </span>中的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">build.gradle </span>文件，查找其中的 <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;background:#E4E4FF\">dependencies </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-hansi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;background:#E4E4FF\">附属</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;background:#E4E4FF\">Module</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-hansi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;background:#E4E4FF\">，将循环引用的附属项去除重新编译即可</span></pre>', ' Android Studio 中对外部工程的概念不叫Proejct 了，而是将外部工程当成一个模块引入到当前工程中，定义为Module  在导入的外部Module 多了，进行编译，难免会遇到各种各样的问题，今天编译的时候就遇到了如下的问题 Error:A problem occurred configuring project \':app\'.&gt; Failed to notify project evaluation listener.  &gt; java.lang.StackOverflowError (no error message) 找了半天，原来是Module过了，导致了Module之间的循环引用问题，知道了问题的原因所在，解决起来就快了，查找每个Module 中的build.gradle 文件，查找其中的 dependencies 附属Module，将循环引用的附属项去除重新编译即可', '', null, '2015-07-27 16:36:45', 'song,2015-08-05 15:17:46', '', '180.213.186.130', '0', '2423', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('40', '', '1', '10', 'AndroidStudio', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Android Studio 编译Could not find property \'Compile\' on project问题', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">刚从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Eclipse </span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">转到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Android Studio </span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">遇到的各种坑，让我很无语，代码都是从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Eclipse</span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">中转过来的，下午的时候为了解决</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Android Studio </span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">的中文乱码问题，找啊找的，乱码问题解决了，但是报了一个</span></p><pre style=\"background:\nwhite\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\ncolor:red\">Error:(26, 0) Could not find property \'Compile\' on project \':Core\'.</span><br /></pre><pre style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">问题原因：</span></pre><pre style=\"background:\nwhite\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Module</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">build.gradle </span><span style=\"font-size:\n10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">中添加了配置</span><br /></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Consolas; background-color: rgb(228, 228, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">tasks</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Consolas;\">.withType(Compile) {<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; options.encoding = </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;color:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&quot;UTF-8&quot;<br /></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Consolas;\">}</span></p><pre style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">解决方法：</span></pre><pre style=\"background:\nwhite\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">Gradle2.0+环境下需将Compile改为JavaCompile</span><br /></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Consolas; background-color: rgb(228, 228, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">tasks</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Consolas;\">.withType(JavaCompile) {<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; options.encoding = </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;color:green;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&quot;UTF-8&quot; </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Consolas;\">}</span></p>', '      刚从Eclipse 转到Android Studio 遇到的各种坑，让我很无语，代码都是从Eclipse中转过来的，下午的时候为了解决Android Studio 的中文乱码问题，找啊找的，乱码问题解决了，但是报了一个Error:(26, 0) Could not find property \'Compile\' on project \':Core\'.问题原因：在Module的build.gradle 中添加了配置tasks.withType(Compile) {   options.encoding = &quot;UTF-8&quot;}解决方法：  Gradle2.0+环境下需将Compile改为JavaCompiletasks.withType(JavaCompile) {   options.encoding = &quot;UTF-8&quot; }', '', null, '2015-07-27 16:51:37', 'song,2015-08-05 15:17:03', '', '180.213.186.130', '0', '1425', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('42', '', '1', '10', 'Eclipse,AndroidStudio', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Eclipse、Android Studio', '<p><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;针对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\nfont-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Eclipse</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\nAR-SA\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Android Studio </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\nAR-SA\">使用发现针对这两款开发环境对中文编码的处理简直弱爆了，开发过程中，任意个环节都会出现乱码问题，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">IDE</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">本身的乱码，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Java </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">中文注释的乱码，有运行效果显示的乱码、有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gradle </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">编译过程中的乱码，折腾了我半天时间、而且无论是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Eclipse </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">还是</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Android Studio</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\nAR-SA\">，使用起来都不是很方便，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\nConsolas;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Android Studio </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\nfont-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gradle </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\nAR-SA\">和M</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">aven </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:\nConsolas;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\nAR-SA\">的引入对于大型项目来说会提高项目编译、项目管理的效率，但是对于小型项目，编译的速度和使用过程中出现的问题，让我真的很头疼，让我无比怀念微软的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Visual Studio</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">啊，微软赶紧加快开源，跨平台的步伐吧</span></p>', '     针对Eclipse、Android Studio 使用发现针对这两款开发环境对中文编码的处理简直弱爆了，开发过程中，任意个环节都会出现乱码问题，有IDE本身的乱码，有Java 中文注释的乱码，有运行效果显示的乱码、有Gradle 编译过程中的乱码，折腾了我半天时间、而且无论是Eclipse 还是Android Studio，使用起来都不是很方便，Android Studio 对Gradle 和Maven 的引入对于大型项目来说会提高项目编译、项目管理的效率，但是对于小型项目，编译的速度和使用过程中出现的问题，让我真的很头疼，让我无比怀念微软的Visual Studio啊，微软赶紧加快开源，跨平台的步伐吧', '', null, '2015-07-27 18:19:09', 'song,2015-08-05 15:16:50', '', '180.213.186.130', '0', '566', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('43', '', '1', '10', '', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Android manifest 配置文件读取顺序', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;今天在做平台启动界面的时候，感觉启动界面变化不大，无非是加载一张图片还是多张图片进行切换的问题。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">想按之前做</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">CS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平台的思路，将启动界面放到一个独立的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Module<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中进行管理，然后在主工程里面配置，让其</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">运行时启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Module</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">里面的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Activity</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为主启动界面，一开始还担心可能安卓不支持这种方式，一尝试，发现这种方法可行，主工程的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">manifest</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">配置如下：</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-color: rgb(190, 237, 190); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&lt;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">application<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">android:allowBackup=</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: green;\">&quot;true&quot;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">android:icon=</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: green;\">&quot;@mipmap/ic_launcher&quot;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">android:label=</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: green;\">&quot;@string/app_name&quot;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&gt;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">activity</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">android:name=</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: green;\">&quot;min.coreui.work.control.SplashFormClass&quot;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">android:theme=</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: green;\">&quot;@style/SplashTheme&quot;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&gt;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">intent-filter</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&gt;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">action<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">android:name=</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: green;\">&quot;android.intent.action.MAIN&quot;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">/&gt;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">category</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">android:name=</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: green;\">&quot;android.intent.category.LAUNCHER&quot;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">/&gt;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">intent-filter</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&gt;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">activity</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&gt;<br /> &lt;/</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: navy;\">application</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&gt;</span></span></p><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>紧接着下一步，配置启动界面的主题，在主启动工程中配置了无标题，全屏，设置<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">APP</span>启动过度图片（避免启动后出现白屏或者黑屏一闪而过的现象），顺利的完成了测试，验证了在主工程的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\"> manifest </span>配置文件中同样可以配置其他<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Module</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Activity</span>。</span></pre><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>不满足这么快就解决问题，在想，<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Module</span>中同样可以配置<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">manifest</span>如果我在<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\"> Module</span>中的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\"> manifest</span>中配置<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\"> Activity </span>效果会是怎么样、如果我主工程、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Module</span>中都配置了<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Activity</span>效果会是怎么样，抱着这种好奇，逐个场景的模拟，发现：</span></pre><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Activity </span>可在自身的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Module </span>中配置属性，也可以在使用它的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Module</span>中配置属性，两种方式都可以。</span></pre><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</span>、如果两个工程中都配置了同一个<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Activity </span>的参数信息，属性不重复情况下，最终运行的时候是整合两个配置的集合作为最终<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Consolas;\">Activity</span>的配置参数，配置重复，则编译报错。</span></pre><pre style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><b>源码地址</b>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Consolas;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/songliuchen/Android\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">https://github.com/songliuchen/Android</span></span></a></span></pre>', '今天在做平台启动界面的时候，感觉启动界面变化不大，无非是加载一张图片还是多张图片进行切换的问题。想按之前做CS平台的思路，将启动界面放到一个独立的Module 中进行管理，然后在主工程里面配置，让其APP运行时启动Module里面的Activity作为主启动界面，一开始还担心可能安卓不支持这种方式，一尝试，发现这种方法可行，主工程的manifest配置如下', '', null, '2015-07-30 11:55:14', 'song,2015-07-31 12:35:08', '', '180.213.76.121', '1', '638', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('45', '', '1', '15', '跨域,同源策略,web', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', '跨域问题（一）:跨域的由来—同源策略', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">从桌面端转到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Web</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">端，在做电商项目的时候，后台数据都是通过服务的形式对外公开，给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">web</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">端、移动段调用，而通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Html</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">方式调用服务，遇到最多的一个问题就是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">js </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">跨域问题，折腾了一两天，把跨域由来、范围、解决方法等系统的看了一遍，通过这几天，总算对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">js </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">跨域有所了解了。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">对于任何基于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">WEB</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的应用，最重要的就是安全性。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">中有各种安全检查以防止恶意脚本攻击你的机器，其中一些特定的安全手段在各种浏览器中都有采用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:Mozilla</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">有个完全独特的完全模型，涉及到了签署脚本和加强特权，我们要知道哪些安全手段是所有浏览器通用的，哪些是特定浏览器的。这样就能创建更安全的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">脚本。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">同源策略</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Same-origin policy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">）</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">这个概念的由来：因为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">JavaScript</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">是世界上最不安全的语言，实际应用中肯定会对它的权限做一些限制。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Same-origin policy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">便是限制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">JavaScript</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">代码权限的一种策略，浏览器都会遵守的。</span><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">因为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">JavaScript</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">太灵活，用得太乱，明明打开的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站，却可能有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">JavaScript</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">的页面上运行！</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">有了同源策略，可以限制来自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">JS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">代码的权限。</span><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">我的理解是，这里</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">JS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">脚本实际上还是可以执行，并不是说完全不能执行。那么同源策略做了什么限制呢？查了网上的资料，好像是说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">HTML”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">的操作会被禁止。比如说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的脚本里面有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">document.write</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">，想修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的页面内容。而又有资料说，这种限制也可以被放宽（一个页面上显示了来自另一个网站的内容，这个确实很常见，没有被禁止）。还有的说法是，打开两个标签页，同源策略是禁止一个标签页的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">JS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">代码访问另一个标签页中的内容。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">同源策略的两个常见用途：一个是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">cookie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">，一个是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">XMLHttpRequest</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Cookie</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的脚本在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站上面执行，可以做很多事情，可以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">getElementById</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">等等，获取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站页面上的信息。那么很自然想到，也可以获取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">cookie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">信息，这就导致用户隐私泄露了。</span><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">解决办法是，浏览器会遵守同源策略，如果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的脚本想获得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网站的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">cookie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">，会被浏览器拒绝执行。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">所以，原理实际上很简单。很多安全漏洞，无非是浏览器说了算，浏览器让你这么干，你就可以这么干，出现漏洞，很简单，改成浏览器不让你这么干就行了。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">XMLHttpRequest</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">即</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Ajax</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">函数只能向当前页面所在域名发送请求。也就是说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">songliuchen.com</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">网页的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Ajax</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">代码，只能与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">songliuchen</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">的服务器通讯，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">songliuchen</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">的服务器获取数据，而不能连到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">slchm</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">去（浏览器会拒绝执行，发送不出这个请求）。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">同源策略的本质是一种约定，可以说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">web</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">的行为就是构建在这种约定之上的。就好比我们人类的行为必须受到法律的约束一样。同源策略的目的就是限制不同源的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">document</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">或者脚本之间的相互访问，以免造成干扰和混乱。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">ajax</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">太灵活了，各种请求说法就发，如果没有同源策略的限制，发到哪里都行，只要你构造好参数和请求路径，那人人都是黑客了，只要知道了地址和参数，可以随时随地获取和修改其他网站的数据，这样会导致各种敏感数据的泄露，随意的攻击导致各种不安全问题。</span></p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 9.35pt; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"232\" style=\"width:174.15pt;border:solid silver 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid silver .75pt;background:#C6D9F1;mso-ba