-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">很多安全漏洞的东西，都是一开始没发现，发现了之后才由厂商制定标准，进行修补的。同源策略便是由网景公司提出并实现。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Netscape Navigator 2.0</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">）</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">后来，肯定又出现了更新颖，更先进的窃取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">cookie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">信息的方法，所以后来微软的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">IE 6.0</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">浏览器又搞出来新的修补措施，就是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">cookie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">HTTP-ONLY</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">属性，不管你是哪个网站，都不让读</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">cookie</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">了。按照网景公司取的名字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Same-origin policy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">，不妨称微软公司这一招为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"> No-origin policy</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">。</span><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">同源策略保证的网络的安全，但是却给我当前项目带来了难题，我服务通过正常的调用获取服务接口数据，跨域问题也就产生了，要想访问非同源策略条件下的地址，获取需要的数据，就必须解决跨域问题。</span></p>', '从桌面端转到Web端，在做电商项目的时候，后台数据都是通过服务的形式对外公开，给web端、移动段调用，而通过Html方式调用服务，遇到最多的一个问题就是js 跨域问题，折腾了一两天，把跨域由来、范围、解决方法等系统的看了一遍，通过这几天，总算对js 跨域有所了解了。对于任何基于WEB的应用，最重要的就是安全性。JS中有各种安全检查以防止恶意脚本攻击你的机器，其中一些特定的安全手段在各种浏览器中都有采用.如:Mozilla有个完全独特的完全模型，涉及到了签署脚本和加强特权，我们要知道哪些安全手段是所有浏览器通用的，哪些是特定浏览器的。这样就能创建更安全的JS脚本。同源策略（Same-origin policy）这个概念的由来：因为JavaScript是世界上最不安全的语言，实际应用中肯定会对它的权限做一些限制。Same-origin policy便是限制JavaScript代码权限的一种策略，浏览器都会遵守的。 ', '', null, '2015-08-02 23:18:12', 'song,2015-10-14 16:22:11', '', '36.106.209.229', '0', '712', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('46', '', '1', '15', '跨域问题,web', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', '跨域问题（二）:跨域的几类解决方案', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Times; font-size: 13.5px; text-align: justify; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">上文已经讲述了跨域问题产生的原因，这边文章想来讲讲跨域问题的几类解决方案，跨域问题的解决方法很多，八仙过海各显神通，但是归根跨域问题的方法分三类：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、通过修改发布的服务头（Header）信息解决</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一般在发布服务时，不会刻意去设置头信息，也就表明只允许当前域名访问，不允许跨域访问，但是在发布服务时可以进行设置。1）设置指定域名可以访问服务，2）可以设置所有域名都可以访问服务。3）更高级一点可以联合代理访问方式，将跨域方法写成一个通用方法，本应用都通过该方法统一调用服务接口。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1510/ujyuo3_跨域问题2.png\" width=\"415\" height=\"227\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 11.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>上图中只要设置Access-Control-Allow-Origin 的值为”*”则表示所有域名都能访问。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">此种方式解决跨域问题，遗留下来的问题就是安全问题，特别是设置了所有域名都能访问时，安全问题就需要考虑了，但是现在即使是普通的服务，后台也会做一些基础的校验，现在的安全问题很少是由于跨域问题引起的。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、通过代理方式解决</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 跨域问题一般只在web 前端调用后台服务才会出现的问题，也就是通过js访问才会出现此类问题，直接通过后台访问其他服务器上服务是不存在该类问题的，这样的话就可以通过代理方式获取跨域数据，1）通过本地后台代码访问服务获取服务数据。2）通过前后台交互，将获取的数据返回到web 前端，达到获取跨域数据的效果。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、通过web JavaScript 其他特性解决</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 该类方法也是仁者见仁、智者见智，利用的javascript的特性也不尽相同，常见的方法如下：</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1）、jsonp 方式（需要后台配合完成）。</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2）、修改 document.domain+iframe方式。</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3）、动态创建script。</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4）、利用iframe和location.hash。</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5）、window.name实现的跨域数据传输。</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6）、使用HTML5 postMessage。</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7）、利用flash等客户端组建完成。</b></p><div><b><br /></b></div>', '       上文已经讲述了跨域问题产生的原因，这边文章想来讲讲跨域问题的几类解决方案，跨域问题的解决方法很多，八仙过海各显神通，但是归根跨域问题的方法分三类：        1、通过修改发布的服务头（Header）信息解决        一般在发布服务时，不会刻意去设置头信息，也就表明只允许当前域名访问，不允许跨域访问，但是在发布服务时可以进行设置。1）设置指定域名可以访问服务，2）可以设置所有域名都可以访问服务。3）更高级一点可以联合代理访问方式，将跨域方法写成一个通用方法，本应用都通过该方法统一调用服务接口。                     上图中只要设置Access-Control-Allow-Origin 的值为”*”则表示所有域名都能访问。此种方式解决跨域问题，遗留下来的问题就是安全问题，特别是设置了所有域名都能访问时，安全问题就需要考虑了，但是现在即使是普通的服务，后台也会做一些基础的校验，现在的安全问题很少是由于跨域问题引起的。        2、通过代理方式解决        跨域问题一般只在web 前端调用后台服务才会出现的问题，也就是通过js访问才会出现此类问题，直接通过后台访问其他服务器上服务是不存在该类问题的，这样的话就可以通过代理方式获取跨域数据，1）通过本地后台代码访问服务获取服务数据。2）通过前后台交互，将获取的数据返回到web 前端，达到获取跨域数据的效果。        3、通过web JavaScript 其他特性解决        该类方法也是仁者见仁、智者见智，利用的javascript的特性也不尽相同，常见的方法如下：        1）、jsonp 方式（需要后台配合完成）。        2）、修改 document.domain+iframe方式。        3）、动态创建script。        4）、利用iframe和location.hash。        5）、window.name实现的跨域数据传输。        6）、使用HTML5 postMessage。        7）、利用flash等客户端组建完成。', '', null, '2015-10-05 16:48:58', 'song,2015-10-14 16:21:55', '', '36.106.209.229', '0', '504', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('47', '', '1', '12', 'dosbox,mac,turbo c,tc', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Mac Turbo C环境搭建', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><b>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Times; text-align: center; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">Mac 安装 Turbo C</span></b></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 说起Turbo C ，相信90之前程序员们都印象深刻，这是我们大学时代必学的开发语言，相信不少同学们都是被Turbo C 代入美妙的编码世界，呵呵，我不是，在大学时代，我都不能算是一个程序员，没写过一行代码，当时让我感兴趣的还是html，觉得，随随变变写几行html标签，就能立马看到效果，不用任何开发工具，操作起来方便，实现起来立竿见影，挺有趣的。后台工作了，才开始编码，工作一年吧，才开始想学学C。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 最近一时兴起，有个功能相用C实现，但现在用的是mac，肯定不能运行只能在dos 上面跑的Turbo C，在网上找了一下，还真有方法可以实现，倒腾了一会儿还真可以了，操作如下：</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、下载dosbox 软件</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 下载地址：<a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1o6CIkLO\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(4, 51, 255);\">http://pan.baidu.com/s/1o6CIkLO</span></span></a></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> &nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; DOSBox 是一个 DOS 模拟程序，由于它采用的是 SDL 库，所以可以很方便的移植到其他的平台。目前，DOSBox 已经支持在 <a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/4821.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Windows</a>、<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/1634.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Linux</a>、Mac OS X、<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/423287.htm\" target=\"_blank\">BeOS</a> 、palmOS、Android 、webOS、os/2等系统中运行</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 好多小时候常玩的游戏都可以通过dosbox 来处理，在电脑上实现重温、dosbox 也是现在普遍使用的对接dos软件、游戏的一款模拟程序。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、下载Turbo C 2.0</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: rgb(4, 51, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(4, 51, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 下载地址：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1kTw9oJP\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(4, 51, 255);\">http://pan.baidu.com/s/1kTw9oJP</span></span></a></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、运行DOSBox 文件下 DOSBox应用程序</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 程序运行后，找到 /Users/<span style=\"color: rgb(12, 49, 247); -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(12, 49, 247);\"><b>songliuchen</b></span>/Library/Preferences/DOSBox 0.74 Preferences （蓝色的替换成自己账户） 文件夹，找到DOSBox 0.74 Preferences 文件并编辑</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4、添加自动运行Turbo C程序</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp;</p><pre><ol class=\"dp-xml\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span>[autoexec]&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>#&nbsp;Lines&nbsp;in&nbsp;this&nbsp;section&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;run&nbsp;at&nbsp;startup.&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>#&nbsp;You&nbsp;can&nbsp;put&nbsp;your&nbsp;MOUNT&nbsp;lines&nbsp;here.&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>mount&nbsp;c&nbsp;/Users/songliuchen/Study/turboc2&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>set&nbsp;<span class=\"attribute\">PATH</span><span>=</span><span class=\"attribute-value\">Z</span><span>:;c:&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>c:&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>tc&nbsp;-r&nbsp;</span></li></ol></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 其中&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1）、/Users/songliuchen/Study/turboc2 表示Turbo C 文件夹路径</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2）、tc -r&nbsp; 表示运行tc程序 ，也可直接使用tc 或者 tc.exe，如果不想一打开就进入Turbo C 开发环境，可以不添加这行命令，等打开程序后再进行输入即可。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1510/mzkhmu_底层开发1.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 11.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;不添加tc - r 效果（在此界面输入 tc -r 同样可进入Turbo C开发环境）</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1510/2z66zf_底层开发3.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 11.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 进入开发界面效果</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5px;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5px;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5</b></span><b>、设置Turbo C开发环境</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 第4步操作完成后，即可开始编写C代码，但是会发现一个问题，编译的时候会报错，要么是找不到头文件、要么是无法生存Obj文件，这是因为未设置配置文件路径所致，设置如下：&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1510/j9u5fp_底层开发4.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6、编写Hello World&nbsp;</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1510/gq5w0l_底层开发5.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.songliuchen.com/Attach/month_1510/apn0hi_底层开发6.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" class=\"Image\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 运行效果</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<b> 7、修改窗体大小</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 在mac 上貌似不能设置窗体全屏，即使可以设置，周边也会留有大片黑屏，只能通过改变窗体大小来改变屏幕大小（可能是没找到正确方法，windows下按Alt＋Enter即可）修改窗体大小方法如下：</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 还是找到第3步中的配置文件，找到windowresolution和output属性配置成如下值，其中&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, mono, serif; line-height: 14px; white-space: pre; font-size: 12px;\">windowresolution属性根据自身配置进行设置</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; min-height: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><pre><ol class=\"dp-xml\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"attribute\">windowresolution</span><span>=</span><span class=\"attribute-value\">1280x680</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span><span class=\"attribute\">output</span><span>=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"attribute-value\">opengl</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li></ol></pre>', ' Mac 安装 Turbo C        说起Turbo C ，相信90之前程序员们都印象深刻，这是我们大学时代必学的开发语言，相信不少同学们都是被Turbo C 代入美妙的编码世界，呵呵，我不是，在大学时代，我都不能算是一个程序员，没写过一行代码，当时让我感兴趣的还是html，觉得，随随变变写几行html标签，就能立马看到效果，不用任何开发工具，操作起来方便，实现起来立竿见影，挺有趣的。后台工作了，才开始编码，工作一年吧，才开始想学学C。        最近一时兴起，有个功能相用C实现，但现在用的是mac，肯定不能运行只能在dos 上面跑的Turbo C，在网上找了一下，还真有方法可以实现，倒腾了一会儿还真可以了', '', null, '2015-10-05 19:24:30', 'song,2015-10-05 21:16:02', '', '58.243.250.186', '0', '785', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('48', '', '1', '10', 'android,http,jdk,HttpURLConnection', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Android 服务请求（一）：JDK Http请求', '<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><b>一、JDK Http Get 请求代码：</b></span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-j\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">    /**&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;执行httpget请求&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;不能在主线程访问web&nbsp;请求，必需单开线程&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;executejdkhttpget()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;Thread()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"annotation\">@Override</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;run()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;executeJDKHttpGet();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}.start();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">/**&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;JDK&nbsp;Http&nbsp;Get&nbsp;请求核心代码&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@return&nbsp;请求结果值&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;String&nbsp;executeJDKHttpGet()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;String&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.net.URL&nbsp;url;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.net.HttpURLConnection&nbsp;connection&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.io.InputStreamReader&nbsp;in&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">try</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">            //服务地址</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;url&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;java.net.URL(</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;www.songliuchen.com&quot;</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection&nbsp;=&nbsp;(java.net.HttpURLConnection)&nbsp;url.openConnection();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 153, 102);\">            //设置超时时间</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller;\"><span style=\"font-family: Menlo;\">             connection</span><span style=\"font-family: Menlo;\">.setConnectTimeout(</span><span style=\"font-family: Menlo; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">10000</span><span style=\"font-family: Menlo;\">);</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>            in&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;java.io.InputStreamReader(connection.getInputStream());&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.io.BufferedReader&nbsp;bufferedReader&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;java.io.BufferedReader(in);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;StringBuffer&nbsp;strBuffer&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;StringBuffer();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;String&nbsp;line;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">while</span><span>&nbsp;((line&nbsp;=&nbsp;bufferedReader.readLine())&nbsp;!=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;strBuffer.append(line);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;strBuffer.toString();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">catch</span><span>&nbsp;(Exception&nbsp;e)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e.printStackTrace();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">finally</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">if</span><span>&nbsp;(connection&nbsp;!=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.disconnect();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">if</span><span>&nbsp;(in&nbsp;!=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">try</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;in.close();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">catch</span><span>&nbsp;(java.io.IOException&nbsp;e)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e.printStackTrace();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">return</span><span>&nbsp;result;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li></ol></pre><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><b>二、JDK Http POST 请求代码：</b></span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-j\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">    /**&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;执行httppost请求&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;不能在主线程访问web&nbsp;请求，必需单开线程&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;executejdkhttppost()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;Thread()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"annotation\">@Override</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;run()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;executeJDKHttpPost();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}.start();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">    /**&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;JDK&nbsp;Http&nbsp;Post&nbsp;请求核心代码&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@return&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;String&nbsp;executeJDKHttpPost()&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;String&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.net.URL&nbsp;url;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.net.HttpURLConnection&nbsp;connection&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.io.InputStreamReader&nbsp;in&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span><span>;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">try</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//服务地址&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;url&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;java.net.URL(</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;www.songliuchen.com&quot;</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection&nbsp;=&nbsp;(java.net.HttpURLConnection)&nbsp;url.openConnection();&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//&nbsp;设置是否从httpUrlConnection读入，默认情况下是true;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.setDoInput(<span class=\"keyword\">true</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//&nbsp;设置是否向httpUrlConnection输出，因为这个是post请求，参数要放在&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//&nbsp;http正文内，因此需要设为true,&nbsp;默认情况下是false;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.setDoOutput(<span class=\"keyword\">true</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//&nbsp;Post&nbsp;请求不能使用缓存&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.setUseCaches(<span class=\"keyword\">false</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//设置请求方式&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.setRequestMethod(<span class=\"string\">&quot;POST&quot;</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//报文头信息&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.setRequestProperty(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Content-Type&quot;</span><span>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;application/x-www-form-urlencoded&quot;</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//编码格式&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.setRequestProperty(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Charset&quot;</span><span>,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"string\">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span><span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 153, 102);\">            //设置超时时间</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span style=\"font-size: smaller;\"><span style=\"font-family: Menlo;\">             connection</span><span style=\"font-family: Menlo;\">.setConnectTimeout(</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: Menlo;\">10000</span><span style=\"font-family: Menlo;\">);</span></span></li><li><span class=\"comment\">            //传参数信息，根据具体情况而定&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.io.DataOutputStream&nbsp;dop&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span>&nbsp;java.io.DataOutputStream(connection.getOutputStream());&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;dop.writeBytes(<span class=\"string\">&quot;username=songliuchen&amp;password=songliuchen&quot;</span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;dop.flush();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;dop.close();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\">//获取服务返回结果，根据情况返回结果需要做判断&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;in&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span>&nbsp;java.io.InputStreamReader(connection.getInputStream());&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;java.io.BufferedReader&nbsp;bufferedReader&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span>&nbsp;java.io.BufferedReader(in);&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;StringBuffer&nbsp;strBuffer&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span>&nbsp;StringBuffer();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;String&nbsp;line;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>&nbsp;((line&nbsp;=&nbsp;bufferedReader.readLine())&nbsp;!=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;strBuffer.append(line);&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;strBuffer.toString();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">catch</span>&nbsp;(Exception&nbsp;e)&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e.printStackTrace();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">finally</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>&nbsp;(connection&nbsp;!=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;connection.disconnect();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>&nbsp;(in&nbsp;!=&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">try</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;in.close();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">catch</span>&nbsp;(java.io.IOException&nbsp;e)&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e.printStackTrace();&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">return</span>&nbsp;result;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li class=\"alt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol></pre><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><b>下载地址:&nbsp;</b></span></span><a href=\"https://github.com/songliuchen/androiddemo\" style=\"background-color: rgb(231, 229, 220);\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">https://github.com/songliuchen/androiddemo</span></span></a></p>', '一、JDK Http Get 请求代码： /** * 执行httpget请求 * 不能在主线程访问web 请求，必需单开线程 */ private void executejdkhttpget() { new Thread() { @Override public void run() { executeJDKHttpGet(); } }.start(); } /** * JDK Http Get 请求核心代码 * @return 请求结果值 */ public String executeJDKHttpGet() { String result = null; java.net.URL url; java.net.HttpURLConnection connection = null; java.io.InputStreamReader in = null; try {  //服务地址 url = new java.net.URL(&quot;www.songliuchen.com&quot;); connection = (java.net.HttpURLConnection) url.openConnection(); ', '', null, '2015-10-08 16:36:19', 'song,2015-10-08 18:14:36', '', '218.241.134.34', '0', '590', '');
INSERT INTO `bt_article` VALUES ('49', '', '1', '10', 'android,http,jdk,HttpURLConnection', '\0', '\0', '\0', '\0', 'Android 服务请求（二）：JDK Https 空证书请求', '<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;一、<b>JDK Https Get 请求代码：</b></span></p><pre><ol class=\"dp-j\"><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">/**</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;执行httpsget请求</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;不能在主线程访问web&nbsp;请求，必需单开线程</span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span><span class=\"comment\">&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">private</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;executejdkhttpsget()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">new</span><span>&nbsp;Thread()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"annotation\">@Override</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"keyword\">public</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"keyword\">void</span><span>&nbsp;run()&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;executeJDKHttpsGet();&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}.start();&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li><span>&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"alt\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;JDK&nbsp;Https&nbsp;Get&nbsp;请求核心代码&n